scenes.label: *start
texts: Hahhh. There's no sign of them at all... Are they really here?
We're not even past the station yet. We gotta head further in.
Stop being a scaredy-cat and get a grip.
The chief'll get mad at you if you don't take this seriously.
Speaking of the chief, it's weird for him to show up at the scene of a crime like this. Usually, he only does that for PR events.
Is this Pollon Takaoka guy a huge threat to society or something?
But for all he did, he didn't actually harm anyone, so he doesn't seem like that much of a bad guy. It's so weird.
Stop looking for excuses to give up the search.
No no no! I want to look for him! I just don't wanna look for him in dark places!
Would a menace like him actually hide somewhere like this anyway? It's not like we're just gonna bump into him—
